
This package implements the Standard eXchange Format (SXF) front end for 
translating SXF files into different accelerator input formats or data
structures.

========================================================================

INSTALLATION

0. add the gperf-2.7.2, bison-1.33, flex-2.5.4 tools in your path 
  (e.g. set path = (/home/ual/tools/gperf/$SXF_ARCH/bin $path)
1. setenv SXF <this directory>
2. setenv SXF_ARCH <linux or sun_gcc>
3. setenv LD_LIBRARY_PATH $SXF/lib/$SXF_ARCH/:$LD_LIBRARY_PATH
4. make

========================================================================

CONTEXT

The package includes the following directories:

Source code.
------------

./src/sxf      - SXF library, the SXF front end;
./src/echo_sxf - EchoSXF library, the SXF demonstration back end.


Documentation.
--------------

./doc/src/html/index.html - entry point of the SXF documentation 

Examples.
---------

./examples/echo  - sxf_tester program and several sxf input files provided 
		   by Hans Grote.
  
